title: Moves teams should make to contend for Super Bowl (Football 5/10)
description:
Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough react to Ziggy Ansah's signing with the Seahawks and Ben Watson's visit with the Pats, before discussing if teams should cut or keep key names. Then, the guys analyze moves that teams should make to increase their Super Bowl chances.
